text: Klara Sierońska-Kostrzewa (28 July 1913 - 20 July 1990) was a Polish gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Chorzów
